Hi Fahimeh,

This can be because of Rhino, Galapagos or Honeybee. You should report this under [Errors and Bugs](http://www.grasshopper3d.com/forum/categories/errors-bugs-and-oversights/listForCategory) with an example file so hopefully David can re-generate the error and tell you why this is happening. I'm not sure if David will see the error here.

Mostapha
